    "description": "<strong>BLINT</strong> - Embark on a gripping sci-fi journey where you take on the role of Fred, an engineer who wakes up in a mysterious elevator with no memory of how he got there. His memories are fragmented and unclear, and now it’s up to you to help him piece together the past and uncover what really happened. Face enigmatic challenges as you explore the unknown and uncover the truth behind the chaos Fred finds himself in.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/42dc9a84dedfc47f89d26e3071012d67.poster.avif?t=1725540004\" width=640 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/42dc9a84dedfc47f89d26e3071012d67.webm?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/42dc9a84dedfc47f89d26e3071012d67.mp4?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Puzzles </strong> - Join Fred on his challenging journey, where he’ll need your wits to overcome a variety of puzzles. Face explicit riddles, where every detail is a crucial clue, and prepare for implicit challenges, where the solution is hidden between the lines, waiting to be uncovered.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/a39505f2b5f80d795494e32086f248a1.poster.avif?t=1725540004\" width=640 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/a39505f2b5f80d795494e32086f248a1.webm?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/a39505f2b5f80d795494e32086f248a1.mp4?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Discover the World</strong> - Explore each floor in search of clues that reveal Fred's story. Dive into forgotten books, mysterious notes, and audio recordings scattered throughout the environment to uncover what happened to Fred and how these events shaped his journey. Every fragment you find is a piece of the puzzle that brings you closer to the hidden truth of his past.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/c2e860101f9622e6f0adf2f0a74c3714.poster.avif?t=1725540004\" width=640 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/c2e860101f9622e6f0adf2f0a74c3714.webm?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/c2e860101f9622e6f0adf2f0a74c3714.mp4?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Short</strong> - An intense and engaging experience, designed to be completed in a single session. Ideal for those seeking a quick, memorable narrative that leaves a lasting impression.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/7a952d72d91aa64ccee27eeb191a15af.poster.avif?t=1725540004\" width=640 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/7a952d72d91aa64ccee27eeb191a15af.webm?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081790/extras/7a952d72d91aa64ccee27eeb191a15af.mp4?t=1725540004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
